{"tid":1603582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 連登熄燈除咗用twitter，可以用噗浪(PLURK)","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T23:57:39.000Z","uid":111002,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5eab35b70b54ca817353484f842721feb4730a94","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"大家都知道連登好快會進入被嚴重DDOS嘅時候，要有方舟計劃，好多人會用twitter，但叫極你班仆街用twitter，都好似便秘痾唔出咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得英文用唔掂嘅，點解唔用噗浪呢？<br />\n人哋由反送中開始到而家一直咁支持個運動，甚至連網站首頁都做咗個short cut俾大家，點解唔用呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PkWX9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PkWX9i.png&h=65cfc407&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DxN4Pj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DxN4Pj.png&h=0ad819eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢會一次過sort哂所有有 hash tag 有反送中嘅，但都係一個可以接收到資訊嘅平台！<br />\n<br />\n噗浪主要用家都係台灣人，又係一個放文宣嘅好地方！<br />\n<br />\n而家同我裝咗佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0933a5c76b49ac64dfa0cda34c5ce46a59cbcc","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"db39f506a742a52d377462a30cea4c174e4aeb1c","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"推 2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d605b5ec591e2c15de31885922517b1f8a8dad5e","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"推 3/10 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f237fd0d6f98757fcd218e0294199691304a4f","tid":1603582,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹下功能"},{"pid":"54ef9dc3968f1fdaed441917d8097c3a2bff6717","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f237fd0d6f98757fcd218e0294199691304a4f","tid":1603582,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹下功能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"其實佢同twitter 個分別唔大，只係個畫面變咗打橫<br />\n呢個係PC 版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGTJDgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGTJDgU.jpg&h=274ec2ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機版會係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7u8Po5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7u8Po5.jpg&h=d11c5dab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你只需要add幾個朋友 or follow 幾個人，就可以keep 住睇到佢哋嘅更新<br />\n<br />\n亦可以係搜尋入面打 #香港加油 #StandWithHongkong #FreedomHongkong 其中一個就可以睇到有關嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n無account 都可以睇到無set權限嘅post"},{"pid":"aaa83eff74d445b098270dd696420571780fbdfa","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"推 4/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8238e7583693204acba68bceaf5b3a8f2a198fc6","tid":1603582,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"推 5/10<br />\n唯一噗浪個問題係未有一個眾合嘅消息中心，但求其搵個冷氣軍師就做到啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97952eba3c2c39c8